name: Listened to Alien Ant Farm feat. DMX Brought Down The F-35

content.html:
SHOW NOTES Ryan has found this show’s equivalent to thinking about the Roman Empire. (Of course it revolves around Tampa.) Sure hope y’all weren’t turning up expecting to hear us talk about anything except the terrible, hilarious continuing misadventures of the F-35! Holly mixes up Beaufort and Other Beaufort like nine times, she’s very sorry, but not like “lost a fighter jet IN THE AIR” sorry Once again, that number is 843-963-3600 Important archaeological news from Buffalo!
